Node.Caption: CWMission04RemindSynopsisTopic: Remind me - what am I supposed to do?

Cell.Text: <<Shared>> Well, well. Look who it is! How have you been?
<<Shared>> I remember you... you were with us at Helgen, and Whiterun. Glad to have you with us. How are you?

Hey there! Can you believe this place? So cold my breath turns to icicles! What are we evening doing up here? | Guess Tullius wants to make sure everything's locked down before launching a serious campaign for Eastmarch. | Anyway, I'm glad you're here. We're out numbered again, more so than when we took that wagon. But if we work together, we can pull this off.
G|Break our men out and head to the courtyard. We'll meet you there.
[S] GS|I can't believe we're the only ones who survived. | Glad you were here. | I guess... I'll hold down the fort by my lonesome. Hurry back and tell them to send a garrison. Quickly!
[S] GS|You go report our success. I'll set up a garrison here. A shame none of the prisoners made it, but their names will be remembered. | Glad you were here. Couldn't have done it without you!
[S] GS|Great work! Get back and report our success. I'll stay here and clean up the mess. | Glad you were here. Couldn't have done it without you!

[S] We found a cave under the lake. With luck, it'll lead into the prison. | I need you to sneak in there, and free our men, killing anyone inside as you go. Once you've rescued the prisoners, head out to the courtyard. | We'll stand guard out here and rush in as soon as we hear fighting. | Should be fun.

[S] There's a grate outside the wall. Looks like it used to be buried in snow.
